nd can be incorporated into end-to-end trainable models such as neural label aggregators or Bayesian Dawid-Skene variants. By combining meta-learning, graph-based inductive bias, and spectral control, our approach offers a principled, adaptive solution to annotator overfitting—a critical bottleneck in reliable machine learning with human feedback.",
